casebody.data:
Johnson, Appellee, v. Cleveland Metropolitan General Hospital, Appellant.

[Cite as Johnson v. Cleveland Metro. Gen. Hosp. (1991), 57 Ohio St. 3d 610.]

(Nos. 90-138 and 90-139 Submitted January 8, 1991— Decided February 6, 1991.) Bilfield & Sandel Co., L.P.A., Martin L. Sandel and Mark L. Behnke, for appellee. Jacobson, Maynard, Tuschman & Kalur Co., L.P.A., Robert C. Maynard, Jerome S. Kalur and Robert C. Seibel, for appellant.

This cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

The court orders that the court of appeals’ opinions not be published in the Ohio Official Reports.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
